"title": "Bug 134488: Set page break for table inside list group header causes data display error", 
"description": "When a page break is set for a table inside a list group header, it causes a data display error.", 
"OB": "1. The table is displayed without any visual issues or data errors.", 
"EB": "1. The table is displayed with a data display error when a page break is set for it inside a list group header.", 
"SR": "Steps to reproduce:\n1. Insert a list with a group.\n2. Insert a table inside the list group header.\n3. Set the 'pageBreakBefore' property of the table to 'always'.\n4. Preview the document in a web viewer, HTML, or PDF format."}
